summary:
- **General Meeting Results**: All resolutions passed, including:  
  - Ratification of Tranche 1 Placement Shares under Listing Rules 7.1 and 7.1A (both >98% approval).  
  - Issue of Placement Shares to Directors (97.1–97.9% approval).  
  - Grant of Performance Rights to Director Michael Hartley (93.8% approval).  
  - Approval of Potential Termination Benefits to Director Michael Hartley (93.0% approval).  

*(No material trading or capital markets impact beyond confirmation of shareholder approvals for previously disclosed transactions.)*
